<% data = adapter.panel_data %>
<% if data[:error] %>
## Token state

_Could not read token state: <%= data[:error] %>_
<% else %>
## Token state (<%= adapter.protocol_name %>)

<% if data[:block_number] %>
_Read at chain block #<%= data[:block_number] %><% if data[:fetched_at] %>, <%= freshness_phrase(data[:fetched_at]) %><% end %>._

<% end %>
- **Symbol:** <%= data[:symbol] %>
<% if data[:name].present? && data[:name] != data[:symbol] %>
- **Name:** <%= data[:name] %>
<% end %>
- **Decimals:** <%= data[:decimals] %>
<% if data[:total_supply_formatted] %>
- **Total supply:** <%= data[:total_supply_formatted] %> (raw: <%= number_with_delimiter(data[:total_supply_raw]) %>)
<% end %>
<% if data[:price_usd] %>
- **Price:** $<%= number_with_delimiter(data[:price_usd].round(6)) %> (via DefiLlama<% if data[:price_observed_at] %>, <%= freshness_phrase(data[:price_observed_at]) %><% end %>)
<% end %>
<% if data[:market_cap_usd] %>
- **Market cap:** $<%= number_with_delimiter(data[:market_cap_usd].round(0)) %>
<% end %>
<% if data[:issuer] %>
- **Issuer:** <%= data[:issuer][:name] %><% if data[:issuer][:url] %> — <<%= data[:issuer][:url] %>><% end %>
<% end %>
<% end %>
